trans-unit.source: Represents the <see langword="<ReferenceList>" /> element used in XML encryption.
trans-unit.target: Reprezentuje <see langword="<ReferenceList>" /> element używany w przypadku szyfrowania XML.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Klasa ta nie może być dziedziczona.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> class represents the `<ReferenceList>` element of an encrypted document XML signature defined by the XML encryption specification.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> Klasy reprezentuje `<ReferenceList>` element podpisu XML zaszyfrowanego dokumentu XML specyfikacją szyfrowania.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> class contains references to <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> and <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> elements that were encrypted by a key contained within another <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> Klasy zawiera odwołania do <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> i <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> elementy, które zostały zaszyfrowane przy użyciu klucza zawarty w innym <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> elementu.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> class uses <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.DataReference> elements to reference <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> elements, and <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.KeyReference> elements to reference <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> elements.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> Klasy używa <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.DataReference> elementy, aby odwołać <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> elementów, i <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.KeyReference> elementy odwołanie do <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> elementów.

trans-unit.source: You can add only <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.DataReference> or <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.KeyReference> objects to the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> collection.
trans-unit.target: Można dodać tylko <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.DataReference> lub <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.KeyReference> obiekty do <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> kolekcji.

trans-unit.source: For more information about XML encryption standards, see http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core.
trans-unit.target: Aby uzyskać więcej informacji na temat standardów szyfrowania XML, zobacz http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core.
